中文: 一天第一个问候送给你，让你有个好心情;第一个祝福送给你，祝你一天工作顺心;第一个愿望送给你，愿你永远幸福又温馨。{val1}!
英文: First greeting of the day to make you happy; first blessing for your work to go smoothly; first wish for you to always be happy and warm. {val1}!
原始翻译: The first greeting of the day will give you a good mood; the first blessing will be given to wish you a good working day; the first wish will be given to you, may you always be happy and warm. {val1}!

中文: 睁开眼睛，给你一个轻轻的祝福，愿它每分每秒都带给你健康、好运和幸福。希望你度过美好的一天!
英文: Open your eyes. Here is my blessing for you to be healthy, lucky, and happy all the time. Hope you have a wonderful day.
原始翻译: Open your eyes and give you a gentle blessing, may it bring health, luck and happiness to you in every moment. Hope you have a great day!

中文: 走过一些路，才知道辛苦;登过一些山，才知道艰难;趟过一些河，才知道跋涉;道一声问候，才知道这就是幸福。{val1}，我的朋友!
英文: Hardship is learned after walking roads, climbing mountains, and crossing rivers. Happiness is here when I greet you. {val1} , my friend!
原始翻译: After walk through some journeys, you know what is difficult; after climbing some mountains, you know what is hard; wading through some rivers, you know how to travel; only when you say hello, you know that this is happiness. {val1}, my friend!

中文: 我一直相信，真正的爱情可以在对方身上唤起某种有生命力的东西，而双方都会因唤醒了内心的某种生命力而充满快乐。
英文: I am convinced that true love can evoke life force in one, while both would be happy for such vitality inside.
原始翻译: I have always believed that true love can evoke something alive in the other person, and that both parties are filled with joy by awakening something alive within.

中文: 一个人要获得实在的幸福，就必须既不太聪明，也不太傻。人们把这种介于聪明和傻之间的状态叫做生活的智慧。
英文: To have happiness, one should be neither too smart nor too stupid. They call this wisdom of life.
原始翻译: To be truly happy, one must be neither too clever nor too stupid. People call this state between smart and stupid as the wisdom of life.

中文: 所谓练习微笑，不是机械地挪动你的面部表情，而是努力地改变你的心态，调节你的心情。学会平静地接受现实，学会对自己说声顺其自然，学会坦然地面对厄运，学会积极地看待人生，学会凡事都往好处想。这样，阳光就会流进心里来，驱走恐惧，驱走黑暗，驱走所有的所有。
英文: To practice smiling is not about mechanically moving your faces, but changing your mindset and adjusting your mood. Learn to accept reality calmly, say let it be to yourself, face bad luck frankly, look at life positively, and always think the best of people. That way the sunlight will come in to drive away fear and darkness, and fill it.
原始翻译: The so-called practice of smiling is not to move your facial expressions mechanically, but to change your state of mind and adjust your mood. Learn to accept the reality calmly, learn to let yourself go with the flow, learn to face adversity calmly, learn to look at life positively, and learn to think about the good in everything. In this way, the sun will flow into the heart, drive away fear, drive away darkness, drive away all of this.

中文: 今天很短，但今天很重要，漂亮的今天，不仅可以把昨天的辉煌变成明天的辉煌，更可以把昨天的失败变成明天的成功。因此，身处今天，不要总是怀念，总是感叹，总是埋怨……我们应该把每一个今天都当成人生的开始!只有从零开始，脚踏实地，全身心的精益好今天，才会迎来灿烂的明天。
英文: Today is short, but it is important. A beautiful today would not only turn yesterday's brilliance into tomorrow's brilliance, but also turn yesterday's failure into tomorrow's success. So stop thinking about the past or signing today... we should live like it is a new start every day! Only by going from zero and live every day to its fullest, we can embrace a brilliant tomorrow.
原始翻译: Today is short, but today is very important. A beautiful today not only turn yesterday's brilliance into tomorrow's brilliance, but also turn yesterday's failure into tomorrow's success. Therefore, in today's world, don't always miss, always sigh, always complain... We should treat every day as the beginning of life! Only by starting from scratch and leaning wholeheartedly, will we usher in today. bright tomorrow.

中文: 不要逃避问题;正视问题。当然，这不容易。在这个世上，任何人都不可能把他所遇到的问题处理得滴水不漏，也没必要马上处理，这不是生活的目的。其实，面对挫折，我们会沮丧，会伤心，会受到伤害，会跌倒。正视问题，和时间一到去学习，去适应，去解决，这才是生活的真正目的。这样，才能塑造一个真正的人。
英文: Do not run away from the problem. Face it. Of course, it is not easy. No one would solve all the problems he encounters perfectly, not should he turn to it immediately. This is not the purpose of life. In fact, we get frustrated, sad, hurt, and down in case of setback. Face the problem and take time to learn, adapt, and solve it is why we live. This can shape a real person.
原始翻译: Don't run away from the problem; face the problem. Of course, it's not easy. In this world, it is impossible for anyone to deal with the problems he encounters without leakage, and there is no need to deal with them immediately. This is not the purpose of life. In fact, in the face of setbacks, we will be depressed, sad, hurt, and fall. Face the problem squarely, and learn, adapt, and solve when the time comes. This is the real purpose of life. In this way, a real person can be created.

中文: 个人总是努力使自己不被群体压倒。如果你努力尝试，你通常会觉得孤独，有时甚至觉得恐惧。但是为保持自我所付出的任何代价都是值得的。
英文: Individuals always work to keep themselves from being overwhelmed by the group. If you try hard, you usually feel alone and even afraid sometimes. But any price paid to stay true to yourself is worth it.
原始翻译: The individual always strives not to be overwhelmed by the group. If you try hard, you often feel lonely and sometimes even frightened. But any price you pay to keep yourself is worth it.

中文: 人生是一段旅程，走过的路，就是你编织的生活，我们无法预知以后的路途。但是，我们能把握现在的自己，珍惜身边的一切，脚踏实地的走，走好自己的路，不要在生命里给自己留下遗憾的风景，生活一直都很简单。
英文: Life is a journey. The path taken is the life you weave, and we cannot predict what is next. But we can seize the day, cherish everything we have, and put our feet on the ground for our destination. Don't make yourself regret. Life is always simple.
原始翻译: Life is a journey, the road you walk is the life you weave, and we cannot predict the future. However, we can grasp who we are now, cherish everything around us, walk our own way, and don’t have any regret in our life. Life has always been simple.

中文: 每天告诉自己要努力，即使看不到未来，即使看不到希望，也依然相信自己。学会放下，很多时候，在意的越多，失去的就越多。看穿但不说穿，很多事情，只要自己心里有数就好，没必要说出来。一定要快乐，想不开就不想，得不到就不要，干嘛非得委屈自己。
英文: Tell yourself every day to work hard. Even if you can't see the future nor hope, you should still believe in yourself. Learn to let it go. In many times, the more you care, the more you lose. In many cases, you only need to know what you are doing, instead of saying it out. You must be happy. If you can’t get something, let it go. Why push yourself so hard?
原始翻译: Tell yourself to work hard every day, even if you can't see the future, even if you can't see hope, still believe in yourself. Learn to let go. Many times, the more you care, the more you lose. See through but don't tell through, many things, as long as you know them well, not need to mention. You must be happy, if you don't want it, you don't want it, if you can't get it, you don't want it. Why do you have to aggrieve yourself.

中文: 你知道什么叫失败?真正失败的人，就是那种特别害怕不能成功。怕死了，连试都不敢试的人。
英文: Do you know what failure means? It is about fearing that you could not succeed. It is someone who is so afraid of death that he/she dares not to give it try.
原始翻译: Do you know what failure is? The person who really fails is the one who is afraid unable to succeed. People who are afraid to die and not even dare to try.

中文: 人生就是一场未知目的地的旅行，更多的时候，我们并不知道自己接下来会遇见怎样的未来。只不过有时候，我们只是一味的狂奔，却忘记了旅行的意义。
英文: Life is a trip to an unknown destination. Most of the time, we have no idea what comes next. Yet sometimes, we hurry along and forget the meaning of travel.
原始翻译: Life is a journey to an unknown destination. More often, we do not know what kind of future we will meet next. But sometimes, we just run without thinking, but forget the meaning of the journey.

中文: 一百种人有一百种命运，有的人可以一条路一直走到底，有的人却注定要曲曲折折，不过谁也不需要羡慕谁。最重要的是：我们迟早会遇上。
英文: Fate varies from people to people. For some, it is a straight road; yet for others, it is full of twists and turns. But we don’t have to envy others. The most important thing is: we will meet sooner or later.
原始翻译: A hundred kinds of people have a hundred kinds of destiny. Some people can go all the way, while others are doomed to twists and turns, but no one needs to be envy. The most important thing is: sooner or later we will meet.

中文: 生命中，有一个人可以去惦念，是缘分;有一个人惦念自己，是幸福。有些事，在不经意间，开始。在不经意里，承诺。在不经意中，产生爱。有些人，在不经意时，分开。于是，各有各的生活，各自爱着别人。曾经的相爱，现在已互不相干。即使在同一个小小的城市，也不曾再重逢。
英文: It is fate to us to miss someone, and it is happiness to be missed by others. Some things begin before we notice. Commitment starts before we now. Love is born secretly. Yet some are parted inadvertently. So, each lives his own life and has his own lover. The love is no longer there. Even in the same small city, we will never meet again.
原始翻译: In life, there is a person who can miss, it is fate; there is a person who miss your ownselves, it is happiness. Some things, inadvertently, start. Inadvertently, promise. Inadvertently, love is born. Some people, inadvertently, separated. So, each has his own life, and each loves others. The love that used to be, is now irrelevant. Even in the same small city, they never met again.

中文: 我们一直寻找的，却是自己原本早已拥有的;我们总是东张西望，唯独漏了自己想要的，这就是我们至今难以如愿以偿的原因。
英文: We have already what we have been looking for; we look around but only miss what we want. This is why we can't get what we want.
原始翻译: What we have been looking for is what we already have; we always look around, but we miss what we want, which is difficult for us to get what we want.

中文: 生活，总有些事让人无奈，人生，总有些情令人悲哀;相信，经历了才会成熟，痛过了才能有更深的领悟。不计较名利，看淡得失，才会体会到真正的乐趣，只有淡泊宁静，才是通透的人生。
英文: Life is always frustrating. We just get sad sometimes. But we will grow after going through these things and get it when our heart aches. Joy is there when we go easy on fame and fortune, gains and losses. We can only have a life to the fullest when we stay calm.
原始翻译: In life, there are always some things that make people helpless, and there are always some feelings in life that make people sad; I believe that you will mature after you have experienced it, and you will have a deeper understanding after pain. Don't care about fame and fortune, look down on the gains and losses, and then you will experience the real fun. Only indifferent and peaceful life can be a transparent life.

中文: 恋爱的纪念物，从来就不是那些你送给我的手表和项链，甚至也不是那些甜蜜的短信和合照。恋爱最珍贵的纪念物，是你留在我身上的，如同河川留给地形的，那些你对我，造成的改变。
英文: A memorial to love is not the watch and necklace you gave me, nor sweet text messages and photos. What to remember in love is the changes you leave on me, like how rivers shapes the land.
原始翻译: The souvenirs of love have never been those watches and necklaces you gave me, or even those sweet text messages and photos. The most precious moment of love is what you left on me, just like what a river leaves to the terrain, the changes you had made to me.

中文: 想要忘记一段感情最好的方法，就是投入到下一段感情。失恋不一定是件坏事，也可能是下一段感情的开始。让我们记住：爱，就疯狂;不爱，就坚强。
英文: The best way to get over a relationship is to commit to the next one. A breakup is not necessarily bad, for it may be the beginning of the next relationship. Remember to love crazily and stay strong in other times.
原始翻译: The best way to forget about a relationship is to jump into the next one. A breakup is not necessarily a bad thing, it can also be the beginning of the next relationship. Let us remember: to love, to be crazy; not to love, to be strong.

中文: 每天在开心中渡过，在快乐中前行。厚爱别人，珍惜家人。款待朋友，诚待她人。真诚的面临社会。宽容的面对人生。谦虚的对待别人。低调的处理事物。不要以清高的眼光看人，不要轻视别人。为人处世。必须要做到自信，自尊，自爱，自力。依赖别人不如依赖自己。珍惜友情，爱情，亲情。珍惜人生的好时光。每过一天，我们就会少一天的时间存留于世。要爱人如己，切记万不可伤害别人。别留后悔在人间，别存遗憾在心中。做一个有良知的人，活着才会淡然无悔。做一个善良之人，活着才会从容。珍惜人生，珍惜光阴。珍惜生命的每时每刻。
英文: Spend every day in happiness. Love others and your family. Treat your friends and others with a sincere heart. Be honest to the society. Be lenient to life. Be honest to others. Stay a low profile. Don't stay lofty nor belittle others. To live in the world, one must be confident, respect and love himself, and work hard on his own. You are the best to rely on. Cherish friendship, love, and family affection. Cherish the good days. Every day spent means one less day left to live. Love others as yourself and never hurt them. Don't leave regrets to others or to yourself. One would not regret only when he stays conscientious. Life will be easy when you remain kind-hearted. Cherish life and the time we have. Cherish every moment of your life.
原始翻译: Pass through every day with joy and move forward with joy. Love others, cherish family. Treat your friends with sincerity. Sincerely face the society. Facing life with tolerance. Be humble towards others. Deal with things quietly. Don't look at people with lofty eyes, and don't despise others. Live for people. Self-confidence, self-esteem, self-love, self-reliance must be achieved. It is better to depend on yourself than to depend on others. Cherish friendship, love, and affection. Cherish the good times in life. With each passing day, we lose a day in the world. Love your neighbor as yourself, and never hurt others. Don't leave regrets in the world, don't keep regrets in your heart. To be a person with a conscience, you will live with no regrets. To be a kind person, you will live calmly. Cherish life, cherish time. Cherish every moment of life.

中文: 在你生命的最初30年中，你养成习惯，在你生命的最后30年中，你的习惯决定了你。
英文: In the first 30 years, you develop habits, and in the last 30 years, your habits define you.
原始翻译: During the first 30 years of your life, you develop habits, and during the last 30 years of your life, your habits define you.

中文: 这个时代的青年，能够把自己安排对了的很少。越聪明的人，越容易有欲望，越不知应在哪个地方搁下那个心。心实在应该搁在当下的。可是聪明的人，老是搁不在当下，老往远处跑，烦躁而不宁。所以没有志气的固不用说，就是自以为有志气的，往往不是志气而是欲望。
英文: Few young ones could have the right plans. The smarter you are, the more desires you have, and the more restless you get. You should have peace of mind. Yet smart ones would think wild and be restless. Not even to mention those without inspiration. Most of the time, they are desire instead of ambition.
原始翻译: There are very few young people in this era who can arrange themselves correctly. The wiser people are, the easier it is to have desires, and the less they know where to put their hearts aside. The mind should be in the present moment. But smart people always stay out of the moment, always run far away, restless and restless. Therefore, it goes without saying that those who have no ambition are those who think they have ambition, and often it is not ambition but desire.

中文: 这是最好的时刻，心怀期待，虔诚敬仰，坚定信念，向世界抬头，淡淡微笑。
英文: This is the best time with a respected, reverent, and faithful heart. Look up and put on a smile.
原始翻译: This is the best time to look forward to the world, look up to the world and smile.

中文: 清晨到夜晚跑，道句{val1}心情好，早睡早起身体好棒，一天心情乐逍遥，上班顺利生活好，烦恼忧愁到九霄，还有祝福身边绕，朋友祝福签个到，幸福常开开心好!
英文: From early morning to night, say {val1}. Early to bed and early to get up for a fit body, a happy day, a smooth work without any worry. Blessings surround you to stay happy all the time!
原始翻译: Day and night, saying {val1} in a good mood, going to bed early and getting up early is good for health, a happy day at work, a smooth life at work, troubles and sorrows gone, and friends blessings around you, happiness always!

中文: 清晨的雨露清澈透明，多事的蝉儿热闹的鸣唱，欢快的喜鹊掩饰不住心中的喜悦，可人的小麻雀也叽叽喳喳，原来你醒了，轻轻的问候一声：{val1}开心一整天。
英文: Reflected in crystal clear morning dews, singing cicadas, happy magpies, and talking sparrows wake you up. A greeting to you: {val1}, happy all the day.
原始翻译: The rain in the morning is clear, the cicadas are lively singing, the cheerful magpies can't hide their joy, and the cute little sparrows are also chirping. It turns out that you are awake, and softly greets you: {val1} happy all day.

中文: 清晨，晶莹的露珠送来丝丝甘甜;清晨，明媚的朝阳送来阵阵温暖;清晨，清爽的微风送来缕缕笑颜;清晨，朋友的短信送来温馨祝愿。朋友，{val1}!
英文: In the morning, crystal dew drops bring sweetness, rising sun sends warmth; refreshing breeze puts on a smile on your face; and a message from friends gives you warm wishes. My friend, {val1}.
原始翻译: In the early morning, the dewdrops bring sweetness; in the early morning, the bright morning sun brings bursts of warmth; in the early morning, the refreshing breeze brings smiles; in the early morning, text messages from friends send warm wishes. Friend, {val1}!

中文: 人生的每一次付出就像在山谷当中的喊声，你没有必要期望要谁听到，但那延绵悠远的回音，就是生活对你最好的回报，新的一天新的开始!{val1}。
英文: Every effort in life is like to shout in a valley. You don’t have to expect anyone to hear it, but the long echo is the best return you have. It means a new day and a new beginning! {val1}.
原始翻译: Every effort in life is like a shout in the valley, you don't need to expect anyone to hear it, but that echo is the best reward life can give you, a new day and a new beginning! {val1}.

中文: 每个早晨，我都在等，等你睁眼发现，发现我在你眼前;每个早晨，我都在等，等你侧耳聆听，聆听一声温柔的{val1}。我要让你每天听见，{val2}!
英文: Every morning, I'm waiting, waiting for you to open your eyes and find that I am before your eyes; every morning, I'm waiting, waiting for you to listen to a gentle {val1}. I want you to hear that every day, {val2}!
原始翻译: Every morning, I am waiting for you to open your eyes and found that I’m in front of you; every morning, I am waiting for you to listen carefully, to hear a gentle {val1}. I want you to hear it every single day, {val2}!

中文: 连夜甜蜜美梦，赶走疲惫忙碌。醒来打开手机，问候抢先登录。朝阳每天依旧，牵挂日久弥新。不论何时何地，祝福永远相随。{val1}!
英文: The sweet dreams chase away tiredness. Wake up and open the phone for sincere greetings. Sun rises every day, and my missing never sets. No matter when and where, you always have my blessing. {val1}!
原始翻译: Sweet dreams all night, drive away tired and busy. Wake up, turn on the phone, and receive greeting. The morning sun is still there every day, and the concern is more and more new. No matter when and where, blessings will always be with you. {val1}!

中文: 甘露为你擦亮晶莹的明眸，阳光为你烘烤温暖的味道，问候为你带来快乐的奇妙，清新的早晨，希望我的一条短信，给你一天简单而充实的幸福，{val1}。
英文: Dews polish your eyes, while sunshine brings warmth. May you be happy with my message in the early morning and spend a simple but happy day, {val1}.
原始翻译: The nectar polishes your crystal clear eyes, the sun bakes the warm flavor for you, greetings bring you a wonderful, fresh morning, I hope that a text message from me will give you a simple and fulfilling day of happiness, {val1}.

中文: 清晨的第一缕阳光照亮心房，清晨的第一段铃声唤醒希望，清晨的第一声问候由我轻轻送上：{val1}，朋友，祝福你一天都有好心情!
英文: The first light of sunshine lights up your heart and the first tinkle of bell rouses hope. Receive the first greeting from me: {val1}, my friend, may you be happy every day!
原始翻译: The sunshine in the morning brighter your mood, the first ringtone in the morning awakens hope, and the first greeting in the morning is gently sent by me: {val1}, my friend, I wish you a good mood all day!

中文: 清新的空气，快乐的气息，透过空气射入你的灵魂里，将阳光呼吸，将幸福抱起，泡一杯甜蜜的咖啡，品尝幸福的意义，接受祝福的信息，祝你{val1}温馨无比!
英文: Fresh air touches you soul as you breathe in sunshine and hugs happiness. Make a sweet cup of coffee and taste happiness. Receive the message of blessing and wish you {val1} happy all the time!
原始翻译: Fresh air, breath with happiness, breathe the sun, hold up happiness, make a cup of sweet coffee, taste the meaning of happiness, receive the message of blessing, I wish a you very warm {val1} !

中文: 清晨太阳升起，明亮你的心情;传达一声问候，温暖你的心情;发条祝福给你，愉悦你的心情。{val1}，愿你天天好心情!
英文: The morning sun gives you a good mood; the greeting makes you warm inside; and the message of blessing keeps you happy. {val1} , I wish you a good mood every day!
